Well - one was an old lady who came to take our - money at school for our savings bank. Miss Oliver. We had to - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6975887 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9004602\charrsid5182558 Did you curtsey to the schoolteacher?
