king about them. He's a real gentleman. Or - there were gentlemen used to have a shotting lodge near us, and he was awfully good to the people in - in the - in the - and - we always treated him as - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6975887 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9004602\charrsid5182558 What was your impression of a policeman when yo
